<td align="center"><b>
<i>Ceratalictus clonius</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Br&#232;thes, 1909&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Augochlora clonia </i>Br&#232;thes, 1909; <i>Oxystoglossa theia </i>Schrottky, 1910; <i>Oxystoglossa thalia pauloensis </i>Schrottky, 1910; <i>Augochlora lorenzinis </i>Strand, 1910; <i>Halictus psorops </i>Vachal, 1911; <i>Ceratalictus lorenzinis </i>&#40;Strand, 1910&#41;</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Halictidae">Halictidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Ceratalictus">Ceratalictus</a>
